orts-2024-03-24/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周日报道，中国已出台指导方针，从政府个人电脑和服务器中逐步淘汰英特尔和 AMD 的美国微处理器。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 05:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-blocks-use-intel-amd-chips-government-computers-ft-reports-2024-03-24/</guid></item><item><title>南海事件后中国誓言维护领土完整</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-safeguard-its-territorial-integrity-after-south-china-sea-incident-2024-03-24/</link><description>中国国防部警告菲律宾不要采取“挑衅”行动，并表示中国将在南海争议海域发生事件的第二天捍卫其领土主权。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-safeguard-its-territorial-integrity-after-south-china-sea-incident-2024-03-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国计划制定市场准入和数据流动新规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-new-rules-market-access-data-flows-premier-li-tells-global-ceos-2024-03-24/</link><description>中国总理李强周日对全球首席执行官和中国政策制定者表示，中国将仔细研究市场准入和跨境数据流动问题，并将很快在这些领域颁布新的法规。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 02:51:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-new-rules-market-access-data-flows-premier-li-tells-global-ceos-2024-03-24/</guid></item><item><title>太阳重返迈阿密，斯瓦泰克追逐“阳光双打”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/pegula-advances-after-zhu-retires-play-resumes-miami-open-2024-03-23/</link><description>经过两天的降雨后，周六迈阿密公开赛迎来了阳光，这对伊加·斯瓦泰克来说是个好兆头，她以 6-1 6-6 的轻快比分，发起了挑战，成为第二位不止一次赢得“阳光双打”的女性选手。 1胜意大利选手卡米拉·乔治。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/pegula-advances-after-zhu-retires-play-resumes-miami-open-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁“纠正错误”赋予中远集团在大型港口的独家经营权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/peru-correct-error-that-gave-cosco-exclusivity-megaport-2024-03-23/</link><description>秘鲁港务局表示，希望纠正一个“行政错误”，该错误导致中国中远海运集团获得了新钱凯巨型港口的独家经营权。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 14:23:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/peru-correct-error-that-gave-cosco-exclusivity-megaport-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度活动人士绝食争取拉达克自治吸引了数千名支持者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-activists-hunger-strike-ladakh-autonomy-draws-thousands-supporters-2024-03-23/</link><description>著名印度活动家索南·旺楚克 (Sonam Wangchuk) 为喜马拉雅山拉达克地区实现自治而进行绝食，他周六表示，禁食已持续到第 18 天，他感到很虚弱，但尽管支持者恳求停止，他仍将按计划继续绝食三天。 。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 09:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-activists-hunger-strike-ladakh-autonomy-draws-thousands-supporters-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>NHK称日本首相承诺增强国防和外交能力以维护和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-pledges-boost-defence-diplomatic-capabilities-preserve-peace-nhk-says-2024-03-23/</link><description>据公共广播公司 NHK 报道，日本首相岸田文雄周六表示，日本将努力加强国防和外交能力以维护和平，并补充说日本各地的军事建设一直在加强。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 07:38:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-pledges-boost-defence-diplomatic-capabilities-preserve-peace-nhk-says-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度在大选前无限期延长洋葱出口禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-extends-ban-onion-exports-indefinitely-ahead-general-election-2024-03-23/</link><description>印度无限期延长对洋葱出口的禁令——这是大选前夕的一个令人惊讶的举动，并将加剧一些海外市场的高价格。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 06:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-extends-ban-onion-exports-indefinitely-ahead-general-election-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警在南海对菲律宾船只使用水炮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-it-took-measures-against-philippine-vessels-south-china-2024-03-23/</link><description>中国海警表示，周六已在南海争议海域对菲律宾船只采取了措施，而菲律宾则谴责这些举措，包括使用高压水枪，称其为“不负责任和挑衅性的”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 02:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-it-took-measures-against-philippine-vessels-south-china-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>天齐锂业在智利SQM-Codelco锂矿交易中寻求股东投票权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tianqi-seeks-shareholder-voting-power-chiles-sqm-codelco-lithium-deal-2024-03-23/</link><description>中国天齐锂业周五敦促智利SQM就与国营铜矿商Codelco讨论的锂交易举行股东投票，并批评谈判缺乏明确性。</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 01:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/tianqi-seeks-shareholder-voting-power-chiles-sqm-codelco-lithium-deal-2024-03-23/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁授予中国金照价值4.05亿美元的港口建设合同</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/peru-awards-chinas-jinzhao-405-million-port-construction-contract-2024-03-22/</link><description>秘鲁政府周五表示，已授予中国金照公司子公司一份在安第斯国家南部建设港口的合同，预计需要 4.05 亿美元的投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 23:34:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/peru-awards-chinas-jinzhao-405-million-port-construction-contract-2024-03-22/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜和中国承诺在北京高层会谈中加强关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-china-held-talks-beijing-kcna-says-2024-03-22/</link><description>朝鲜媒体周日称，朝鲜和中国官员在北京会面，承诺进一步发展双边关系，平壤在因新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 封锁后寻求扩大外交接触。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 21:35:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-china-held-talks-beijing-kcna-says-2024-03-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>